。”界面新闻的评论文章，反思了将“第一学历”等同于能力的错误思维，强调应当在过程中评价人才，而不能让人以为取得第一学历便“高枕无忧”或“无力回天”。北大一博导因“第一学历”遭嫌弃，学历偏见怎么破？"},"attached_info":"Cj8I+cfNrbKB7qdiEAMaCDcxNTAzMTMyIMDShosGMG84oBVAEHIJNDkxNDk1OTUweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"51 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-31e1bf03ac3353e9dcd7cc85c16a4c53_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"17_1633907258.1436708","card_id":"Q_442763529","target":{"id":442763529,"title":"有什么让你吃一次就记一辈子的美食？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/442763529","type":"question","created":1612373878,"answer_count":860,"follower_count":4366,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[304,532,53651,119860,192010],"comment_count":17,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"比如好吃的，好喝的，菜品，特产，异国美味等等不限"},"attached_info":"Cj8I+cfNrbKB7qdiEAMaCDYwNjY5NzQzIPa+64AGMBE4jiJAEXIJNDQyNzYzNTI5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"48 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-fc9c8921ebb29d3bb43e4c8227ed18cb_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1633907258.144087","card_id":"Q_491341758","target":{"id":491341758,"title":"酒店员工偷开顾客百万路虎出事故车损 26 万，酒店建议顾客报警，将配合走司法途径，谁该为此事负责？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/491341758","type":"question","created":1633744710,"answer_count":233,"follower_count":1544,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[570,1066,11793,24721,119972],"comment_count":41,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"住了一夜酒店，却损失 20 多万，姜先生郁闷极了。 姜先生经常往返于甘肃和西安之间做生意，10 月 4 日晚，他到达西安后，入住太华北路上的美豪丽致酒店（西安北大明宫店），因停车场较远，酒店有代客泊车服务。姜先生办理入住的时候，将车钥匙交给前台，随即上楼休息。员工偷开顾客百万路虎出事故车损26万，酒店：建议顾客报警"},"attached_info":"Cj8I+cfNrbKB7q